        oa:hasTarget narr:FocusSequencing ;
        narr:principal narr:Actor_Session ;
        skos:note "This is the second time she has made this exact move — the March 19 MVP redefinition (install–compile–cite–remember–review as core; Refraction, Registry, marketplace deferred) was MVP v1's version of it, and the July 11 MVP-cut decision record was its immediate predecessor. Second run of the Mar 19 MVP scope decision, amending the Jul 11 MVP-cut record — the strip-down move is becoming aswritten's recurring discipline." ;
        narr:extends narr:Narrative_MVPScopeDecision ;
